      "name": "deposit",
      "docs": [
        "Deposit `value` lamports against `precommitment = Poseidon(nullifier, secret)`.",
        "The program assigns `label = Poseidon(scope, leafIndex)` and inserts",
        "`commitment = Poseidon(value, label, precommitment)`."
